=begin pod

=NAME    Math::Factoral::Operator
=AUTHOR Ribbon Otter 
=VERSION 0.1.0

=head1 Description 
Provides a postfix operator for integers, !, which calculates the factorial. It
binds tighter than the exponent, **. Thus, 5**2! = 5**2  and not 25!.

=head1 Installation

Install this module through L<zef|https://github.com/ugexe/zef>:

=begin code :lang<sh>
zef install Math::Factoral::Operator
=end code

